import sys; print('Python %s on %s' % (sys.version, sys.platform)) sys.path.extend([WORKING_DIR_AND_PYTHON_PATHS]) sys.path.append("/sandbox/lib/jumpscale") from Jumpscale import j # import pudb # import traceback
# default is 12 lines or get from config LOGGER_PANEL_LINES = j.core.myenv.config.get("LOGGER_PANEL_NRLINES", 12) j.core.myenv.debug = False j.core.myenv.config["LOGGER_INCLUDE"] = ["*"] j.tools.logger.reload() j.tools.logger.debug = False # j.application.bcdb_system # needed to make sure we have bcdb running, needed for code completion j.application.interactive = True # n = j.data.nacl.get(load=True)
j.shell(loc=False, locals_=locals(), globals_=globals())
